  "prompt": "How can I search someone's follower list for a specific user on Instagram?",
  "response": "Unfortunately, Instagram does not provide a direct built-in search function within a user's follower list. To find a specific user in someone's followers, you would typically need to:\n\n1. Go to the user's profile\n2. Tap \"Followers\"\n3. Manually scroll through the list\n4. Use the search bar at the top to filter followers\n\nIf the list is long, this can be time-consuming. There are some third-party apps and websites that claim to offer advanced follower search, but be cautious as these may violate Instagram's terms of service or compromise account security.",
